---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About The Tech Teacher.">
  <section class="section container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1 style="max-width:none; font-size:clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);">A practical education technology notebook</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-layout">
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p>
          For more than twenty years, I've worked at the intersection of education, technology, and innovation.
        </p>
        <p>
          I've been a teacher, school leader, education consultant, and technology specialist, working with schools to navigate everything from classroom technology and digital strategy to professional learning and artificial intelligence.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm also a parent of two boys, which means I experience technology from another perspective entirely. The questions schools are asking about AI, social media, screen time, digital wellbeing, and online safety are often the same questions parents are asking around the dinner table.
        </p>
        <p>
          This blog is a collection of ideas, experiments, reflections, and practical lessons gathered from both worlds.
        </p>
        <p>
          You'll find posts about educational technology, AI, Apple ecosystems, digital workflows, teaching and learning, school leadership, and occasionally parenting in a digital age. Some ideas come from working alongside schools. Others come from trying to help my own children develop a healthy and productive relationship with technology.
        </p>
        <p>
          The education technology world is an interesting and ever-changing space. To navigate it successfully, we need honest conversations about what works, what doesn't, and what genuinely improves learning.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's what you'll find here.
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="profile-card" aria-label="Wihan Neethling profile">
        <img
          src="/assets/wihan-neethling-profile.jpg"
          alt="Wihan Neethling outside De Hoek Manor"
          width="1200"
          height="900"
        />
        <div class="profile-card-body">
          <p class="profile-name">Wihan Neethling</p>
          <p class="profile-roles">Educator | Consultant | Speaker | Parent</p>
          <div class="credential-list">
            <div class="credential-item">
              <h2>From the classroom</h2>
              <p>Teacher, school leader, and innovator who has lived the challenges educators face.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="credential-item">
              <h2>Alongside schools</h2>
              <p>EdTech specialist supporting strategy, technology adoption, and professional learning that sticks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="credential-item">
              <h2>At home</h2>
              <p>Dad to two teenage boys, exploring the real conversations about technology in family life.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="profile-mission">Different spaces. Same mission. Better people. Better learning. Better futures.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
